  <title>A RESTful entity web API for Drupal 8</title>
  <link>https://klau.si/restful-entity-web-api-drupal-8</link>
  <description>&lt;span class="field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden"&gt;A RESTful entity web API for Drupal 8&lt;/span&gt;

            &lt;div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field__item"&gt;&lt;p&gt;I'm happy to announce that I will join the &lt;a href="http://groups.drupal.org/wscci"&gt;WSCCI initiative&lt;/a&gt; to help develop web service interfaces in Drupal 8. Big thanks to my team at &lt;a href="http://epiqo.com/"&gt;epiqo&lt;/a&gt; for sponsoring and making time for me to work on this, as well as &lt;a href="https://www.acquia.com/"&gt;Acquia&lt;/a&gt; for providing a crucial financial part to make this happen.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Read the &lt;a href="http://groups.drupal.org/node/262063"&gt;full announcement on groups.drupal.org&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
